BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ minute} = 60 \text{ seconds} `]. Do the following unit conversions. Use mixed numbers (like 1 1/2) in your answer when needed.

a. [`` [$min1Display] \text{ minutes} = ``] [__________]{$sec1} [`` \text{ seconds} ``]

